  "vulnerability_information": "## Summary:\n- Target URL:\n`https://www.opn.ooo/th-en/` (Footer Section)\n- Affected Component:\n- The Facebook icon in the footer links to: `https://www.facebook.com/Opnglobal`\n-This link is broken (leads to a \u201cDeleted account\u201d error).\n\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n- Go to https://www.opn.ooo/th-en/\nClick on facebook icon\n- You will redirected to a https://www.facebook.com/Opnglobal available for takeover\n- Check here https://brandsnag.com/facebook-username-checker for username\n\n## Impact\n\n- Users can be misled into trusting a fake Facebook page.\n- An attacker can post fake updates, run scam ads, or collect user data.\n- The organization loses control over its social media presence.",
